Tampa police are investigating after a body was found floating in the water near the Courtney Campbell Causeway early Monday morning. Police said they were called to the south side of the causeway at about 6:35 a.m. to a report of a body in the water. Officers responded and found the body of a male floating in the water, police said in a news release. No other details were immediately released. This is a developing story. Stay with tampabay.com for updates.